{"tid":2362638,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"AVA61納米樓撻訂戶減價最多5%重推，價錢仲平過2017年","createTime":"2021-01-11T14:48:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T16:12:59.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"92f8857990c077efd11e5d36ee3cba0b65ca9848","tid":2362638,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T14:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2845000/2849604/0110_AVA61_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2845000%2F2849604%2F0110_AVA61_1024.jpg&h=ddb62e0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n納米樓繼續成為市場焦點，二手市場不少納米樓業主蝕走外，一手市場的發展商亦要睇住市場走，長沙灣AVA 61早前錄得3伙撻訂單位，發展商今日減價重推AVA 61撻訂戶，計及調整價錢及調整折扣後，個別單位實際減價最多5%。<br />\n<br />\nAVA 61最新價單顯示，3伙撻訂單位面積161至232平方呎，最新定價333萬至560萬元，較2017年最初定價減價3.2%至11.1%。不過當年即供最高8%折扣，而今次重推即供折扣收窄至2%，計算折實樓價後，個別AVA 61撻訂單位最新價錢實際比2017年平5%。。<br />\n<br />\n然而， 164平方呎的5樓B室單位，最新折實樓價326.3萬元，則貴過2017年價錢約3%。"},{"pid":"7820e831742cd5b35087e76dfff4f3a87fea5d0e","tid":2362638,"uid":9633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T15:22:56.000Z","msg":"嘩仲咁撚貴搵邊個接先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd51a68db27430986b84025683842119391b85f","tid":2362638,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7820e831742cd5b35087e76dfff4f3a87fea5d0e","tid":2362638,"uid":9633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T15:22:56.000Z","msg":"嘩仲咁撚貴搵邊個接先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T16:12:59.000Z","msg":"你定啦<br />\n<br />\n大把水魚接"}]}